SUMMARY:AI Essentials for Jobs: Boosting Your Job Search Strategy
DTSTAMP:20260326T215655Z
DTSTART:20260331T203000Z
DESCRIPTION:Tuesday\, March 31\, 2026\, 1:30 - 3pm\n\nDiscover how to effec
	tively use Artificial Intelligence \\(AI\\) to enhance your job search and
	 all aspects of your application and interview preparation.\n\nLocation Li
	nk:\n\nCentral Library\n\nRoom Location: Level 4 - Room 2\n\nRegistration 
	Required: Registration is not required.\n\nDetailed Description: Join Empl
	oyment Specialist\n\nCorey Minatani\n\nfrom Evergreen Goodwill&'s Job Trai
	ning and Education Center \\(JTEC\\) for an introductory workshop designed
	 to help you leverage artificial intelligence to enhance your job search.\
	, Learn how AI can streamline resume building\, job matching\, interview p
	reparation\, and networking\, making your job hunt smarter and more effici
	ent. Whether you're new to AI or looking to sharpen your digital tools\, t
	his session will provide practical strategies to boost your chances of suc
	cess in today&'s competitive job market.\, Thanks to our partner\n\nEvergr
	een Goodwill Job Training & Education.\n\nEvent Logistics: There will be t
	ime after the presentation to ask questions.\, Find out more about our\n\n
	Employment Workshops .\n\nContact Us: If you have questions about this eve
	nt\,\n\nAsk Us\n\nor call 206-386-4636.\n\nADA Accommodations: We can prov
	ide accommodations for people with disabilities at Library events. Please\
	n\ncontactLEAP\n\nat least seven days before the event to request accommod
	ations.\, All Library programs are free and open to the public.\,\n\nhttps
	://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/ai-essentials-for-jobs-boosting-y
	our-job-search-strategy/18161400/2026-03-31T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - All Even
	ts
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/ai-essentials-for-jobs-bo
	osting-your-job-search-strategy/18161400/2026-03-31T00
